          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="infoLabel_SM">
            <property name="text">
             <string>You can sign messages/agreements with your addresses to prove you can receive firos sent to them. Be careful not to sign anything vague or random, as phishing attacks may try to trick you into signing your identity over to them. Only sign fully-detailed statements you agree to.</string>
            </property>
